{"id": "1493507096577183815", "channel_id": "1493507096577183815", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "谁将葬身异处？谁又将长眠故土？\n命运落下了熟悉的判决，是黑底白字的讣告。\n预知，照见了结局，却照不明灰蒙蒙的命途。\n选择此刻的崩解，还是尽头的毁灭？\n\n命运的主人，终究也是命运的奴仆……\n作网自缚的囚徒，来不及哭或是笑，\n手中的纺轮转动着，永不停歇。\n「命运的囚笼里，我们都一无所有。」\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nWho will be buried beneath a foreign sky?\nWho in the soil of home shall forever lie?\nFate hands down its familiar verdict:\nA white-on-black obituary, nothing more.\nPrescience illuminates the end,\nBut leaves the grey and murky road unlit.\nShall we choose oblivion now,\nOr devastation at the end?\n\nThe Master of Fate is its servant too...\nA prisoner bound within her self-made web.\nNo time to weep, no time to laugh—\nStill her hands turn the spindle, never to rest.\n*\"Within this cage of fate, we come with naught—\nand naught is all we share.\"*", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T07:03:59.844000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 44}, {"emoji": "love", "emoji_id": "1356053099931897977", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1493507097063849984", "filename": "CG_.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3445947, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1493507096577183815/1493507097063849984/CG_.png?ex=69df385f&is=69dde6df&hm=8f353b07cae7805b3f9a80f413412e67dd0b52ac2d8f880194f23c3f9bda7bf1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1493507096577183815", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.0 无期囚徒┊Perpetual Thrall", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
